About Us
Privacy Policy



Effective Date: 03/30/2024



Devil x Detail ("we," "us," or "our") is committed to protecting the privacy and personal information of our customers. This Privacy Policy outlines how we collect, use, and safeguard your information when you interact with our website, mobile applications, and other online services (collectively, the "Services"). By accessing or using our Services, you agree to the terms of this Privacy Policy.





Information We Collect

We may collect the following types of information:



1. Personal Information You Provide:

・ Account Information: When you create an account, we collect your name, email address, phone number, shipping and billing addresses, and password.

・ Purchase Information: When you make a purchase, we collect payment details (e.g., credit card information) and order details.

・ Communication Information: When you contact us or sign up for updates, we collect your email address, phone number, and any messages you send.



2. Automatically Collected Information:

・ Device Information:** Your IP address, browser type, operating system, and device identifiers.

・ Usage Data:** Information about your interactions with our Services, such as pages viewed, time spent on our site, and links clicked.

・ Cookies:** We use cookies and similar tracking technologies to enhance your experience and collect data for analytics and marketing purposes.



3. Information from Third Parties:

We may receive information about you from our payment processors, shipping providers, and other third-party services that facilitate transactions and improve our Services.



How We Use Your Information

We use the information we collect for the following purposes:



・ To Provide Our Services: Process your orders, manage your account, and deliver products.

・ To Improve Our Services: Analyze usage patterns to enhance the user experience and improve site functionality.

・ To Communicate with You: Send updates about your orders, respond to inquiries, and share marketing communications (if you have opted in).

・ For Security: Protect against fraud, unauthorized access, and other illegal activities.

・ To Comply with Legal Obligations: Meet regulatory requirements and enforce our terms and policies.



How We Share Your Information

We do not sell or rent your personal information to third parties. However, we may share your information in the following ways:



・ Service Providers: With third parties who perform services on our behalf, such as payment processors, shipping providers, and marketing platforms.

・ Legal Compliance: When required to comply with legal obligations, respond to lawful requests, or protect our rights.

・ Business Transfers: In connection with a merger, acquisition, or sale of assets, your information may be transferred as part of the business transaction.



Your Choices



1. Marketing Communications:

You can opt out of receiving marketing emails by clicking the "unsubscribe" link in any email or contacting us directly.



2. Cookies:

Most browsers allow you to manage cookie preferences. Disabling cookies may affect the functionality of our Services.



3. Access and Updates:

You can access and update your personal information by logging into your account or contacting us.



Security

We use industry-standard security measures to protect your information. However, no online transmission or storage system is completely secure. You use our Services at your own risk.



Children's Privacy

Our Services are not intended for children under 13 years of age. We do not knowingly collect personal information from children.



Changes to This Policy

We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Any changes will be posted on this page with the updated effective date. We encourage you to review this Privacy Policy regularly.



Contact Us

If you have any questions or concerns about this Privacy Policy or our practices, please contact us at:  hello@devilxdetail.com
